EZ-Shop Order Receipt
========================================
Order ID: #<%= @order.orderid %>
Date: <%= @order.createdAt.in_time_zone('Asia/Kuala_Lumpur').strftime('%B %d, %Y %I:%M %p') %>
Payment Method: <%= @order.paymentMethod.to_s.gsub('_', ' ').upcase %>

Billed To:
----------------------------------------
<%= @customer.name %>
Phone: <%= @customer.phone %>
Address:
<%= @customer.shoppingAddress %>

Items Ordered:
----------------------------------------
<% @order_items.each do |item| %>
* <%= item.product&.name %> (Size: <%= item.product&.size %>)
  Qty: <%= item.quantity %> @ <%= number_to_currency(item.unitPrice) %> each
  Subtotal: <%= number_to_currency(item.subtotal) %>
<% end %>

Summary:
----------------------------------------
Subtotal:          <%= number_to_currency(@order.subtotal) %>
<% if @order.item_discount > 0 %>
Discount:         -<%= number_to_currency(@order.item_discount) %>
<% end %>
Shipping:          <%= @order.shipping_cost == 0 ? "FREE" : number_to_currency(@order.shipping_cost) %>
----------------------------------------
Total Paid:        <%= number_to_currency(@order.finalTotal) %>

========================================
Thank you for your purchase!
If you have any questions or concerns, please reply to this email or contact support.
